<P>According to a Calculation made by &s;eve|ral <HI>Italian</HI> Writers; but as to my own Opi|nion, I cannot believe that <HI>A&s;ia</HI> could fur|ni&s;h half tho&s;e numbers, and therefore do rather follow the Computation of the <HI>A&s;ia|ticks,</HI> according to this Account:
