<P>The <HI>Turks</HI> on their Side, had a far greater Lo&s;s; which, tho' it cannot be di&s;tinctly certified, however may be gue&s;&s;ed at, by what will appear from the following LIST of &s;everal of their Great and Smaller Officers, found Dead on the Field of Battle, and which were known and Named by a <HI>Turki&s;h</HI> Pri&s;oner, to be, <HI>viz.</HI></P>
<LIST>
<ITEM>THE Great Viziers <HI>Kapit&s;chler Chi|haia&s;i.</HI></ITEM>
